{"title":"歌唱总路线","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":6,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱总路线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗红心跳蹦蹦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片灯火一片红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗红心跳蹦蹦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跳得瓦刀点头笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跳得红砖满天跑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跳得砖墙随风长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转眼烟囱入云霄；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心啊心啊为啥跳？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总路线宣布了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"富拉尔基建筑工人  朱迪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东风起　红旗飘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总路线，总路线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人看了心头甜；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多快好省加油干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义在眼前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东风起，红旗飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总路线光芒在照耀；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓足干劲争上游，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掀起技术革命新高潮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上海中国铅笔一厂工人　朱宝林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜过红太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总路线胜过红太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳每天下山坡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总路线日夜放光芒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安徽民歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"追月亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人动刀枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日夜上战场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实现总路线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"登上光荣榜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安徽民歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"技术大革命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满山遍野响歌声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃进花开朵朵红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要想实现总路线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来个技术大革命。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安徽民歌"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1}